comments: Sabonis (SAC) makes marginal contact to Jokic's (DEN) body as he briefly places a resting arm on the back of Jokic during his post up.
Jokic (DEN) extends two hands into Sabonis' (SAC) body and the contact affects his SQBR during the drive.
Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position on Sabonis (SAC) as he beats him to the spot, firms up and absorbs the contact to the front at the end of his drive.
Jokic (DEN) absorbs the contact initiated by Sabonis' (SAC) to the front of his body and legally contest the finish near the rim.
Sabonis (SAC) makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) body on the drive that affects his SQBR.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact to Sabonis' (SAC) body that does not affect his SQBR at the end of his drive.
Sabonis (SAC) leaves the floor with possession of the ball, and then returns to the floor prior to release the ball during his pass attempt.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fox (SAC), but extends his lower body into Fox and the contact dislodges him.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Sabonis' (SAC) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) holds Jokic's (DEN) arm and the contact affects his FOM during the rebound.
Fox (SAC) makes more than marginal contact to Jokic's (DEN) body as he makes the pass to his teammate in the back court.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Jokic (DEN) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful, and the call was overturned. Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during Barnes' (SAC) shot attempt near the rim.
